jalse.listeners

Interface AttributeListener<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Attribute type to trigger for.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AttributeAdapter

    public interface AttributeListener<T>
    Listener for AttributeType value manipulation. When attributes are added, updated or removed the suitable defined method will be triggered. A change is a manual fire of the trigger to denote a internal state change of the attribute. Unique AttributeEvent will be supplied for each trigger.
    Author:
    Elliot Ford
    See Also:
    AttributeContainer, DefaultAttributeContainer
